                  as.person("Bibhas Chakraborty"),
                  as.person("Marcus Eng Hock Ong"),
                  as.person("Benjamin Alan Goldstein"),
                  as.person("Nan Liu")),
  journal      = "JMIR Medical Informatics",
  year         = "2020",
  volume       = "8",
  number       = "10",
  pages        = "e21798",
  url          = "https://doi.org/10.2196/21798",
  textVersion  = "Xie F, Chakraborty B, Ong MEH, Goldstein BA, Liu N. AutoScore: A Machine Learning-Based Automatic Clinical Score Generator and Its Application to Mortality Prediction Using Electronic Health Records. JMIR Med Inform. 2020;8(10):e21798. Published 2020 Oct 21. doi:10.2196/21798")
